title: #74 - QuarterJade Talks Joining OfflineTV & BrookeAB’s Wild Girl’s Night
itunes:title: #74 - QuarterJade Talks Joining OfflineTV & BrookeAB’s Wild Girl’s Night
description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast, streamer QuarterJade along with BrookeAB come onto the show to talk about joining OfflineTV, playing Valorant and dealing with its toxicity, how she met her boyfriend Masayoshi, Brooke's epic girl's night, and more!
